---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import site from "../config/site";
import style from "../styles/archive.module.css";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me - AI & Data Science Graduate"
  description="Learn about Kishore Kumar A's journey in AI, machine learning, and data science. Building intelligent systems and real-world AI solutions."
  pageType="about"
  includeLocalBusiness={true}
  path="/about/"
>
  <main class={style.main}>
    <div class={style.title}>
      <h1 class={style.heading}>
        <span>About Me</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class={style.content}>
      <p>
        I'm an AI and Data Science graduate specializing in building AI agents, fine-tuning LLMs, and implementing RAG pipelines. 
        Experienced in developing real-world AI solutions across voice automation, multi-agent systems, and deep learning, 
        with a hands-on, build-first approach (Vibe-Coder). Also passionate about STEM and space research.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        My work with Aurora AI focuses on delivering AI-driven solutions that help businesses streamline. 
        However, my true passion lies in the mysteries of the cosmos. I've been deeply fascinated by 
        space exploration and cosmology, and I envision a future where AI, quantum computing, and other 
        advanced technologies play a pivotal role in humanity's journey to explore the universe.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        From following groundbreaking space missions to pursuing knowledge in astrophysics and quantum 
        mechanics, I'm driven by the desire to contribute to humanity's next giant leap. My long-term 
        goal is to launch a space or deep tech startup that bridges the gap between scientific discovery 
        and practical applications that can help us venture further into the stars.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        <strong>What I can help you with:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul style={{ marginLeft: "3ch" }}>
        <li><strong>AI Solutions:</strong> Building intelligent systems for automation, customer support, and business processes using cutting-edge AI technologies.</li>
        <li><strong>Space Tech Innovation:</strong> Exploring how AI and deep tech can contribute to space exploration and cosmic research.</li>
        <li><strong>Deep Tech Integration:</strong> Combining AI, quantum computing, and other advanced technologies for breakthrough solutions.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>
        Ready to explore the future of AI and space technology?
      </p>
      
      <div style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="btn"
          style={{ fontSize: "larger", marginBottom: "4em" }}
        >
          Let's Connect & Collaborate
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>